Metrics required for monitoring : 
CPU   - Done
Memory - Done
SWAP   - Done
Load Avg  - Done
Number of processes - done
Disk Usage - done
Inode usage - done
Network in and out - /sys/class/net/INTERFACE/statistics/rx_packets 
Count of open ports - done




CPU Source : /proc/stat
CPU calculation from /proc/stat : https://rosettacode.org/wiki/Linux_CPU_utilization#Python

IO calculation : https://www.kernel.org/doc/Documentation/ABI/testing/procfs-diskstats
docker run -v /Users/lalwanh/metrics-manager:/app -it metrics-manager /bin/bash